msgid ""
"Gitdown tries to find and understand your articles in a given repository in "
"a few different ways. This process is called \"Resolving\" and it entails "
"three steps, that you should follow when editing the settings."
msgstr ""
"Mae Gitdown yn ceisio dod o hyd i'ch erthyglau a'u deall mewn ystorfa "
"benodol mewn ychydig wahanol ffyrdd. Gelwir y broses hon yn \"datrys\" ac "
"mae'n golygu tri cham, y dylech eu dilyn wrth olygu'r gosodiadau."

msgid "Repository"
msgstr "Ystorfa"

msgid ""
"Before you can get started you have to specifiy where your repository is "
"located. By default there is an example repository that you can use to test "
"and learn how this plugin works."
msgstr ""
"Cyn y gallwch chi ddechrau mae'n rhaid i chi benodol lle mae'ch ystorfa. Yn "
"ddiofyn mae yna ystorfa enghreifftiol y gallwch ei defnyddio i brofi a dysgu"
" sut mae'r ategyn hwn yn gweithio."

msgid "Glob Pattern"
msgstr "Patrwm glob"

msgid ""
"With the glob pattern you specifiy where in your repository the files are. "
"For example: <code>**/*.md</code> will match any file that ends with .md. "
"Use <a href=\"https://globster.xyz/\">globster.xyz</a> to learn and test "
"your glob pattern or you can try it out right down below this paragraph."
msgstr ""
"Gyda'r patrwm glob rydych chi'n ei nodi lle mae'r ffeiliau yn eich ystorfa. "
"Er enghraifft: bydd <code> **/*. Md </code> yn cyfateb i unrhyw ffeil sy'n "
"gorffen ag .md. Defnyddiwch <a href=\"https://globster.xyz/\"> globster.xyz "
"</a> i ddysgu a phrofi'ch patrwm glob neu gallwch roi cynnig arno i lawr "
"islaw'r paragraff hwn."

msgid "Resolver Function"
msgstr "Swyddogaeth Resolver"

msgid ""
"As of now you dont have to worry too much about the resolver function as "
"there are only two: Simple and Directory to Category. They will both look "
"for Front matter info within the markdown files and fill out meta "
"information about the post this way."
msgstr ""
"Ar hyn o bryd does dim rhaid i chi boeni gormod am y swyddogaeth Resolver "
"gan mai dim ond dau sydd: syml a chyfeiriadur i'r categori. Bydd y ddau "
"ohonyn nhw'n edrych am wybodaeth mater blaen yn y ffeiliau marcio ac yn "
"llenwi gwybodaeth meta am y post fel hyn."

msgid "User Interface"
msgstr "Rhyngwyneb defnyddiwr"

msgid ""
"The user interface is pretty straight forward. Gitdown inserts three "
"different UI element into your page you see description of them below."
msgstr ""
"Mae'r rhyngwyneb defnyddiwr yn eithaf syml. Mae Gitdown yn mewnosod tair "
"elfen UI wahanol yn eich tudalen rydych chi'n gweld disgrifiad ohonyn nhw "
"isod."

msgid "Article Overview"
msgstr "Trosolwg o'r erthygl"

msgid ""
"This is where you currently are. Here you see all the posts within the repo "
"that have been found via the glob pattern and resolver. You can publish, "
"update and delete posts here. Keep in mind that posts are identified by "
"their slug."
msgstr ""
"Dyma lle rydych chi ar hyn o bryd. Yma fe welwch yr holl swyddi o fewn y "
"repo a ddarganfuwyd trwy'r patrwm glob ac ail -wneud. Gallwch gyhoeddi, "
"diweddaru a dileu swyddi yma. Cadwch mewn cof bod pyst yn cael eu nodi gan "
"eu gwlithod."

msgid ""
"You can enter a complex view mode where you see more infos about the "
"articles which may be useful when setting up."
msgstr ""
"Gallwch chi fynd i mewn i fodd gweld cymhleth lle rydych chi'n gweld mwy o "
"wybodaeth am yr erthyglau a allai fod yn ddefnyddiol wrth sefydlu."

msgid ""
"Deleting a post means it will be deleted on Wordpress not in the repository,"
" so it is advised to make a backup of your posts beforehand."
msgstr ""
"Mae dileu post yn golygu y bydd yn cael ei ddileu ar WordPress nid yn yr "
"ystorfa, felly fe'ch cynghorir i wneud copi wrth gefn o'ch swyddi ymlaen "
"llaw."

